The SDSS filters have been converted from ascii files available at https://svo2.cab.inta-csic.es/svo/theory/fps/index.php?mode=browse&gname=SLOAN&asttype=

The page itself refers to http://filters.apo.nmsu.edu/curves/SDSS/ which in turn references the following paper - http://filters.apo.nmsu.edu/curves/SDSS/photo_system.pdf

An ADS record of the publication can be found at https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996AJ....111.1748F/abstract

Kepler_Kepler.K.dat added on 11/14/2025 by Sanchit Sabhlok. The file itself was made by Gudmundur Stefansson by extracting data from https://keplergo.github.io/KeplerScienceWebsite/data/documentation/KSCI-19033-001.pdf Figure 13. 
